------------------------------------------------------------------------
r79 | (no author) | 2013-11-22 16:04:10 +0530 (Fri, 22 Nov 2013) | 6 lines
Merged via: r80

** Heater sensor, cold junction sensor, and sample temperature sensor have been respectively renamed to sensor 1, sensor 2, and sensor 3. This is required as either sensor 2 or sensor 3 can be used as sample temperature sensor.

In the present implementation, sensor 2 (a Pt100) is being used as sample temperature sensor. The tcon.py module has been updated accordingly.

-- Krish

