r64 | (no author) | 2013-09-28 20:55:24 +0530 (Sat, 28 Sep 2013) | 11 lines
Merged via: r74, r66

** TCON communication speed changed to 9600 and parity set to none.

** Three new function, namely readHeaterTemperature, read_CJ_Temperature, and readSampleTemperature, have been implemented. They read temperature directly from the hardware. This is a consequence of Pt100 and TC calibration, where all calculations need to be done on firmware, and the final results are transferred to the computer.

** Time axis in temperature plot was buggy. Fixed.

TODO:
	-- Graphical calibration interface to be implemented.

-- Krish

